description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Full Remote (Senior) Senior MS Dynamics 365 Developer with \\+8 years of experience.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Basic configuration and setup for the new/existing Service desk/Business unit;
* Customizable configuration using form editor, business rules, workflows, PowerApps and Power Automate;
* Enhanced customizations using Plugins, Custom Workflows, jQuery, JavaScript, XRM controls, UCI framework;
* Creating dashboards and reports using standard OOB feature or Power BI;
* Building Custom Application using PowerApps;
* Configuring queues and routing rules like skill, content area, agent availability for auto triaging
* Building multiple channel capabilities like Email, Web, portal, etc.;
* Building Self Service/Custom Portal with knowledge management capabilities to help users in raising the queries and to check the status of their queries;
* Building Integrations with ESB Service, Flat files, and other internal applications;
* Perform unit testing and support integration testing and fix defects and issues in a timely manner;
* Support and maintain the production environment, fix issues raised by the business users;
* Testing should cover Test cases for Regression Testing, Performance Testing and Load Testing;
* Support and maintain the production environment, fix issues raised by the business users;
* Analyze and document the impact of any new change request or fix requested by the business users
* Provide troubleshooting/technical support;
* Actively participate in design and analysis sessions to ensure sound team decision\\-making;
* Support system and user acceptance testing activities, including issue resolution;
* Complete technical documentation to ensure system is fully documented;
* Share best practices and lessons learnt from past implementation efforts;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* The Dynamic 365 Developer needs to be well versed with Dynamics 365 Customer Service, Customer Service Hub, Knowledge Management, Self Service Portal, Reports \\& Dashboards using Power BI/SSRS, Power Automate and Power Apps;
* \\+8 years of relevant experience in design and development of MS Dynamics, Power Platform based solutions;
* Proficient with developing, deploying, customizing and integrating Dynamics 365 Customer Service;
* Proficiency in designing, developing and implementing business processes, plugins and workflows;
* Experience in designing and creating custom entities and relationships between those entities;
* Experience in handling multiple business unit with data segregation and cross BU access/roles;
* Strong hand on experience in developing Dynamics Self\\-service Portals and Custom portal integrating multiple Dynamics instance for Case creation, Case status update, Add Comment, Upload Screenshots and knowledge Management integrating SharePoint;
* Experience of software development using Microsoft .Net, C\\#, JSON and jQuery;
* Experience in Customer Service Hub, Unified Client Interface, Client API form context and Model\\-driven apps;
* Strong Hand on experience in developing scheduled Reports, Custom SSRS reports with multiple data sources (external \\& internal);
* Experience in developing automations using Power Automate and Power Apps;
* Experience in developing application which can be published to Azure;
* Experience in handling huge volumes of case and email records;
* Experience in using third party tools to configure, customize, monitor and troubleshoot the Dynamics application
* Experience in Agile/Scrum based process implementation using tools like Azure DevOps with pipeline automation for CI/CD;
* Experience in designing and automating the survey forms using MS Forms Pro is a plus;
* Experience in developing self service portals using Power Apps/Portals is a plus;
* Experience in developing Power BI Dashboards \\& Reports is a plus;
* Dynamics 365 Customer Service Insights, AI Powered Dashboards, AI Predictive analytics and other AI\\-driven insights is a plus;
* Fluent in English;
